title: Hand crafted 'Made in India'
body: What's not to like about an Indian made product especially one crafted so nicely. Surfaces of the cork are very nicely shaped and finished. The fit in a wine bottle is tight ensuring there is no leakage. I bought these to bottle my home made wines. Manufacturer takes great pride in their product and it shows. Don't choose another, go for this one when you need corks for wine bottle.
